        <p><strong>Up & Alta</strong> (“we,” “us,” “our,” or “Company”) knows that you care about how your personal information is used and shared, and we take your privacy seriously.</p>

        <h2>Information Collection And Use</h2>
        <p>Our primary goals in collecting and using information are to provide and improve the Service, to administer and assist you in administering your Account on the Service, and to provide you with a better experience with the Service.</p>
        
        <p>We may collect Personal and Non-Personal information such as:</p>
        <ul>
